placeDesc: Just off the Nebo Scenic Loop sits the Devil’s Kitchen. This location features an amazing trail and scenic overlook that displays the various formations of the Devil’s Kitchen.
placeShortDesc: A dazzling display of red rocks weathered into spires and hoodoos.
